 ng\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi tr\u1ebb c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p v\u1eeba v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/chan-dung-nu-tong-thong-ham-mo-bong-da-cua-croatia-188-191355.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/chan-dung-nu-tong-thong-ham-mo-bong-da-cua-croatia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/hau-truong/chan-dung-nu-tong-thong-ham-mo-bong-da-cua-croatia-188-191355.html\">Ch\u00e2n dung n\u1eef t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Croatia</span><br>\r\nN\u1eef t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn khi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1372","checkdouble":"191507"},{"date":"11:52 18/07","title":"Luis Enrique t\u1ef1 tin t\u00e1i thi\u1ebft T\u00e2y Ban Nha","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/10/luis-enrique-tu-tin-tai-thiet-tay-ban-nha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00e2n HLV 48 tu\u1ed5i tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi b\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga lo\u1ea1i ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f4i ra m\u1ed5 x\u1ebb ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 ph\u00e1t sinh ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c, khi HLV Julen Lopetegui b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ebfc sau khi ngang nhi\u00ean \u0111i \u0111\u00eam v\u1edbi Real Madrid.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2n HLV Luis Enrique c\u1ee7a TBN t\u1ef1 tin t\u00e1i thi\u1ebft \u0110TQG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2n HLV Luis Enrique c\u1ee7a TBN t\u1ef1 tin t\u00e1i thi\u1ebft \u0110TQG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/luis-enrique-la-lua-chon-dung-dan-cho-dt-tay-ban-nha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00e2n HLV Luis Enrique c\u1ee7a TBN t\u1ef1 tin t\u00e1i thi\u1ebft \u0110TQG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau khi c\u00fai \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc, L\u0110B\u0110 La Roja l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c b\u1eaft tay t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng thay th\u1ebf v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nhanh ch\u00f3ng, Luis Enrique ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m v\u00e0o gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng. HLV 48 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00e1i t\u00ean xa l\u1ea1 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u khi t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng vang d\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng Barcelona, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u00fa \u0103n ba l\u1ecbch s\u1eed La Liga, Copa del Rey v\u00e0 Champions League \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2014-15.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Luis Enrique tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin t\u00e1i thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng bao l\u00e2u, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i n\u1eafm l\u1ea5y m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u00fat do d\u1ef1, c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc. D\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi n\u00e0y r\u1ed3i, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0a T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u1eddi v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 l\u00e0m chu\u1ea9n m\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 theo c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nghe theo ai hay \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i n\u00e0o h\u1ebft. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ri\u00eang v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt h\u1ee3p l\u00fd nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Luis Enrique s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng T\u00e2y Ban Nha trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, khi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 \u00f4ng h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Wembley ng\u00e0y 8/9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Anh. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft cho HLV 48 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Euro 2020 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eb1m g\u1ee1 g\u1ea1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u th\u1ee9 ba trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-luis-enrique-tro-thanh-hlv-truong-dt-tay-ban-nha-180-190800.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Luis Enrique tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/luis-enrique-la-lua-chon-dung-dan-cho-dt-tay-ban-nha-180-190812.html\">Luis Enrique l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn cho \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1371","checkdouble":"191508"},{"date":"07:04 18/07","title":"\u201cBrazil c\u1ee7a Tite v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 gi\u1ecfi l\u1eafm r\u1ed3i\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/brazil-cua-tite-vao-tu-ket-world-cup-da-la-gioi-lam-roi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Brazil t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Anh tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Tite c\u00f2n c\u1ea3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Brazil d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft WC 2018</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018, \u0110T Brazil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i ba bao g\u1ed3m \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00e0u l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed l\u00e0 Neymar, Selecao t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chinh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 6.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCho t\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Brazil v\u1eabn su\u00f4n s\u1ebb. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t \u0110T B\u1ec9 v\u1eeba t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u1eeba c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i cay \u0111\u1eafng d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Brazil t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Brazil t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/buffon-that-bai-tai-world-cup-2018-se-giup-neymar-manh-me-hon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Brazil c\u1ee7a Neymar d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Renato Augusto khi v\u00e0o thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 Brazil l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 khi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Samba bao g\u1ed3m 1 b\u00e0n ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Fernandinho, 1 t\u1eeb c\u00fa s\u00fat xa tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Kevin De Bruyne.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kaka l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 Brazil c\u1ee7a Tite</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kaka kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi \u0110T Brazil, kh\u00f4ng v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World cup c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. Nh\u01b0ng x\u00e9t m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, ng\u00f4i sao l\u1eebng danh m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Real Madrid v\u00e0 AC Milan tin r\u1eb1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Selecao v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7y t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Tite\" title=\"HLV Tite\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Brazil-bi-loai-khoi-World-Cup-Tite-dang-trach-1,-Neymar-dang-trach-10-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Brazil v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin \u1edf HLV Tite</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;<em>T\u1ea1i Brazil, lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft</em>&rdquo;, Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Brazil tr\u00ean Omnisport. &ldquo;<em>Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i th\u00edch nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra. T\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</em>.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;<em>G\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. Hai HLV \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 cho ch\u00fang ta nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng may m\u1eafn. C\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Thiago Silva ch\u1ea1m c\u1ed9t v\u00e0 \u0111i ra ngo\u00e0i. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, pha b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Kompany ch\u1ea1m Fernandinho v\u00e0 \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.</em>&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;<em>Brazil c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfm khuy\u1ebft, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa. N\u1ebfu Tite ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9nh l\u1ea1i ch\u00fang t\u1eeb gi\u1edd cho \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2022. Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c, t\u00f4i tin Selecao \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</em>.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Brazil tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/neymar-fairplay-gui-loi-chuc-chien-thang-den-ca-phap-va-croatia-421-191144.html\">Neymar g\u1eedi t\u00e2m th\u01b0 ch\u00fac chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/neymar-khien-huyen-thoai-brazil-that-vong-tran-tre-421-191030.html\">Neymar khi\u1ebfn huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Brazil th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/an-tuong-world-cup/dung-lac-loi-nua-hoi-cac-vu-cong-samba-471-190954.html\">B\u00e0i d\u1ef1 thi \u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng World Cup: \u0110\u1eebng l\u1ea1c l\u1ed1i n\u1eefa h\u1ee1i c\u00e1c v\u0169 c\u00f4ng Samba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/trao-luu-moi-dau-ruot-voi-thu-thach-neymar-tren-toan-the-gioi-421-190849.html\">Tr\u00e0o l\u01b0u m\u1edbi: \u0110au ru\u1ed9t v\u1edbi &ldquo;Th\u1eed th\u00e1ch Neymar&rdquo; tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/fernandinho-bi-doa-giet-vi-ban-phan-luoi-trong-tran-brazil-thua-bi-188-190755.html\">Fernandinho b\u1ecb d\u1ecda gi\u1ebft v\u00ec b\u00e0n ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi trong tr\u1eadn Brazil thua B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1370","checkdouble":"191472"},{"date":"07:36 18/07","title":"M\u1eb9 Ronaldo: \u201cKh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/me-ronaldo-khong-the-tro-lai-mu-la-dieu-dang-tiec.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cristiano Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 v\u00e0 m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a CR7 c\u0169ng m\u1edbi x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c r\u1eddi Real Madrid. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn c\u00f9ng ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Los Blancos, si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u00e1nh m\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed5 d\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Manchester United. C\u0110V c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 M.U v\u00e0 Ronaldo hy v\u1ecdng l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 cu\u1ed9c t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed di\u1ec5n ra. Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, CR7 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 6 n\u0103m ch\u01a1i cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u cao qu\u00fd v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng c\u00e1c Manucians.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i MU nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i MU nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/Cristiano-Ronaldo-khong-the-tro-lai-MU-nhu-du-dinh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c, M.U \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ee9ng ngo\u00e0i trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Sau \u0111\u00f3, Juventus nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 99 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, Maria Dolores Aveiro t\u1eebng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 tr\u00ean b\u00e1o r\u1eb1ng mu\u1ed1n th\u1ea5y anh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man United. Tuy nhi\u00ean, gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y b\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n con trai m\u00ecnh khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng Alexis Sanchez hay Romelu Lukaku trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"ba Aveiro va Ronaldo\" title=\"ba Aveiro va Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/ba-Aveiro-va-Ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">B\u00e0 Aveiro ti\u1ebfc khi Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e0 Aveiro tin r\u1eb1ng Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn nh\u1ea5t cho m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c phi\u00eau l\u01b0u m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Italia. &ldquo;Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ee9ng ph\u00eda sau n\u00f3&rdquo;, Aveiro n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;S\u1eafp t\u1edbi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Ronaldo. T\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng n\u00f3 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u1eady.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Ronaldo k\u00fd v\u1edbi Juventus c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2022. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 CLB l\u1edbn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a CR7 b\u1edfi khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac giao k\u00e8o n\u00e0y, anh s\u1ebd 37 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ronaldo-tiet-lo-soc-ve-vu-chuyen-nhuong-toi-juventus-184-191410.html\">Ronaldo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/kaka-phat-bieu-ve-viec-ronaldo-toi-juventus-176-191405.html\">Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u1edbi Milan l\u00e0&hellip; \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-real-noi-gi-khi-ronaldo-toi-juventus-180-191404.html\">HLV Real n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/mourinho-ronaldo-se-phuc-hung-bong-da-y-176-191396.html\">Mourinho: &ldquo;Ronaldo s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5c h\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1369","checkdouble":"191474"},{"date":"07:56 18/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 18/7: \u201cG\u0103ng tay v\u00e0ng\u201d World Cup ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t t\u1edbi Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-187-gang-tay-vang-world-cup-tien-sat-toi-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 18/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Boca Juniors mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n &ldquo;ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba&rdquo; c\u1ee7a Barca. </strong>Boca Juniors r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Colombia. G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 Argentina m\u1edbi g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 n\u0103m gi\u00e1 5 tri\u1ec7u Euro k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t t\u1edbi Barcelona.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Courtois ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t t\u1edbi Real Madrid. </strong>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Chelsea, Thibaut Courtois \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi Real Madrid. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 35 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111o\u1ea1t G\u0103ng tay v\u00e0ng World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 187 Courtois ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t t\u1edbi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 187 Courtois ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t t\u1edbi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/world-cup-2018-khep-lai-voi-nhung-danh-hieu-ca-nhan-xung-dang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Real chi t\u1edbi 35 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Courtois</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Blind ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ajax. </strong>Man United x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Daley Blind \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ajax v\u1edbi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 14 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng H\u00e0 Lan t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Old Trafford v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2014. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi chia tay sau 4 n\u0103m, Blind c\u00f9ng M.U \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh 1 c\u00fap FA, 1 c\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n v\u00e0 1 Europa League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Liverpool chi \u0111\u1eadm cho Alisson.</strong> Liverpool \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n v\u1edbi Alisson khi \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh b\u00e2y gi\u1edd n\u1eb1m \u1edf cu\u1ed9c th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd v\u00e0 AS Roma. Liverpool \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 72 tri\u1ec7u Euro (62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) cho Alisson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng tuy\u1ec3n Anh ph\u1edbt l\u1edd Bayern.</strong> Jordan Pickford m\u1edbi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi t\u1eeb g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 \u0110\u1ee9c, Bayern Munich \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Everton. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, gi\u00fap \u0110TQG l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia trong hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Pickford\" title=\"thu mon Pickford\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/David-Moyes-phat-bieu-ve-Jordan-Pickford-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pickford t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Bayern \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Everton</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>M\u1eb9 Ronaldo: &ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc&rdquo;.</strong> Cristiano Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 v\u00e0 m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a CR7 c\u0169ng m\u1edbi x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>&ldquo;Brazil c\u1ee7a Tite v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 gi\u1ecfi l\u1eafm r\u1ed3i&rdquo;.</strong> Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Brazil t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Anh tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Tite c\u00f2n c\u1ea3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c CSKA \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Golovin cho Chelsea. </strong>CSKA ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Golovin cho Chelsea. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh Evgeniy Giner, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CSKA Moscow x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1368","checkdouble":"191475"},{"date":"08:43 18/07","title":"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 danh s\u00e1ch t\u1eadp trung \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/19/hlv-le-thuy-hai-noi-gi-ve-danh-sach-tap-trung-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i cho r\u1eb1ng n\u00ean g\u1ecdi th\u00eam 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn khi ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua 17/7, L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam/vff-cong-bo-danh-sach-30-tuyen-thu-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191430.html\" target=\"_blank\">danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam </span>\u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018. Trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 26 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i U23 v\u00e0 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u00ean 23 g\u1ed3m \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m, Nguy\u1ec5n Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i cho r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng Park n\u00ean g\u1ecdi th\u00eam m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Viet Nam mat co hoi doi dau nguoi Uc\" title=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1ea5t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dac\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/croatia-viet-tiep-cau-chuyen-20-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7n g\u1ecdi th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i l\u00ean h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng Olympic VN</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u t\u1eebng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Becamex B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng cho hay: &quot;Theo t\u00f4i, HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 sau v\u00f2ng 20, V.League 2018 xem th\u1eed c\u00f3 th\u00eam g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t n\u00e0o n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt hay kh\u00f4ng r\u1ed3i g\u1ecdi th\u00eam t\u1eeb 1 \u0111\u1ebfn 2 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i l\u00ean h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 1 th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi di\u1ec5n ra, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu. \u0110\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u1ea1n \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd danh s\u00e1ch r\u1ed3i ch\u1ed1t 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed9n. L\u00e0m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u00f4ng Park c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u00f4ng H\u1ea3i &ldquo;l\u01a1&rdquo; c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng Park c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m, th\u00ec nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea7n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u1eebng quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb CLB n\u00e0o, hay CLB th\u00ec 8 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi nh\u01b0ng CLB kh\u00e1c l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1. G\u1ecdi ai v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 quy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng. \u0110i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang ta quan t\u00e2m l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nh\u01b0 n\u00e0o, ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n ra sao \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ASIAD v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin cao nh\u1ea5t&rdquo;, HLV L\u00ea Thu\u1ef5 H\u1ea3i cho bi\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 25/7 t\u1edbi 3/9/2018. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia d\u1ef1 ASIAD, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ki\u1ec3m nghi\u1ec7m l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn ra 20 c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ASIAD.</p>\r\n<h2>Danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam:</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n: Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng (S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC), B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng (FLC Thanh H\u00f3a), \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m (H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng)&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1eadu v\u1ec7: Hu\u1ef3nh T\u1ea5n Sinh (Qu\u1ea3ng Nam FC), Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh (SLNA), Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, \u0110\u1ed7 Duy M\u1ea1nh, Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Chung, \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC), V\u0169 V\u0103n Thanh, L\u00ea V\u0103n S\u01a1n, Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy (HAGL), B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Nguy\u1ec5n Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i (Viettel), Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i (H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7: Ph\u1ea1m \u0110\u1ee9c Huy, Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i, \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC), L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Tri\u1ec7u Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng, Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng (HAGL), L\u00ea Ph\u1ea1m Th\u00e0nh Long (H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng), Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c (SLNA)&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o: Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC), Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n, Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng (HAGL), Ho\u00e0ng Minh Tu\u1ea5n (Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh), H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh (SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng), Nguy\u1ec5n Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh (B.B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng).&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-guong-mat-bi-hlv-park-hang-seo-bo-quen-tai-asiad-2018-168-191462.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2015/10/1/hang-thu-dtvn-can-lam-bong-dang-mot-nhu-thanh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-guong-mat-bi-hlv-park-hang-seo-bo-quen-tai-asiad-2018-168-191462.html\">Nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t b\u1ecb HLV Park Hang Seo &lsquo;b\u1ecf qu\u00ean&rsquo; t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nL\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u00e9m duy\u00ean ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u1edf gi\u1ea3i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-bu-tottenham-canh-tranh-hcv-asiad-cung-lua-cong-phuong-168-191451.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/29/sao-bu-tottenham-canh-tranh-hcv-asiad-cung-lua-cong-phuong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-bu-tottenham-canh-tranh-hcv-asiad-cung-lua-cong-phuong-168-191451.html\">Sao b\u1ef1 Tottenham c\u1ea1nh tranh HCV ASIAD c\u00f9ng l\u1ee9a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nCh\u00e2n s\u00fat Tottenham v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c L\u0110B\u0110 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191444.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/22/thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191444.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec t\u1eeb danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\nChi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 17/7, danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1. V\u00e0 nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb b\u1ea3n danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u00fat ra \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec?</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1367","checkdouble":"191477"},{"date":"08:53 18/07","title":"HLV Croatia: \"T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Brazil ho\u1eb7c Barca\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/16/hlv-croatia-toi-co-the-dan-dat-brazil-hoac-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Zlatko Dalic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 51 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0110T Brazil v\u00e0 Barca nh\u01b0ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Croatia lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c \u01b0a th\u00edch.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dalic v\u00e0 Croatia \u0111i s\u00e2u \u1edf World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/bai-hoc-tu-nguoi-croatia-dat-nuoc-nho-giac-mo-lon-421-191456.html\" target=\"_blank\">Croatia \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn</span>. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D, b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Argentina. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 3-0.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Zlatko Dalic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Zlatko Dalic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/hlv-croatia-toi-co-the-dan-dat-brazil-hoac-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Dalic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng Croatia \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCroatia c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh khi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Nga tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Anh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft d\u00f9 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 5 nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Dalic \u0111\u00e3 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1eafng 2-1 sau 120 ph\u00fat.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i t\u1ed1n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c \u1edf 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 2-4. D\u00f9 sao v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u00e1 qu\u00e2n c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ngo\u00e0i mong \u0111\u1ee3i v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCroatia tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 trong s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3n ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng v\u1ea1n NHM. HLV Dalic ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y 51 tu\u1ed5i cho th\u1ea5y t\u00e0i n\u0103ng trong vi\u1ec7c truy\u1ec1n s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt hay nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Dalic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, HLV Dalic l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh c\u00f3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 51 tu\u1ed5i, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Dalic mu\u1ed1n ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Guong mat duom buon cua HLV Dalic\" title=\"G\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3m bu\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a HLV Dalic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/hlv.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0HLV Dalic c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Brazil ho\u1eb7c Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nZlatko Dalic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 51 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0110T Brazil v\u00e0 Barca nh\u01b0ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Croatia lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c \u01b0a th\u00edch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Brazil ho\u1eb7c Barcelona, t\u00f4i tin m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi \u0110T Croatia, t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cV\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7i \u0111au khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1m h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn chung k\u1ebft. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Croatia s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1366","checkdouble":"191480"},{"date":"20:37 17/07","title":"Rami: \"Pogba \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/rami-pogba-da-tro-thanh-mot-nha-lanh-dao-thuc-su.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung v\u1ec7 Adil Rami cho r\u1eb1ng Pogba \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o sau khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Man United gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u0103ng quang \u1edf World Cup 2018.</h2><h2>Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pogba \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. V\u00e0 anh c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00e2ng cao v\u00e0 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Man United \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Croatia \u0111\u00e3 minh ch\u1ee9ng cho m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Pogba. V\u00e0 Pogba \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i xung quanh c\u1ea7n anh nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<h2>Rami ca ng\u1ee3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rami khen Pogba \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Rami khen Pogba \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/rami-pogba-da-tro-thanh-mot-nha-lanh-dao-thuc-su.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pogba \u0111ang d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Pogba l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf Moscow, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Rami chia s\u1ebb: <em>\u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n r\u1eb1ng Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u th\u00edch nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m c\u00e1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt kh\u00f3 nh\u01b0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u00e2y gi\u1edd Pogba \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n trong kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. K\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, Pogba \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn l\u1ed1i cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nPogba s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb World Cup 2018. Man United hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i ICC. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 10/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Pogba:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-duoc-khuyen-nen-trao-bang-doi-truong-cho-pogba-172-191419.html\">Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u00ean trao b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng cho Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cac-huyen-thoai-mu-ca-ngoi-pogba-cho-phep-doi-kieu-toc-421-191349.html\">C\u00e1c huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU ca ng\u1ee3i Pogba, cho ph\u00e9p... \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1365","checkdouble":"191460"}]}